{"tid":819083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳女童拒為國歌站立惹議","createTime":"2018-09-14T14:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T06:04:49.000Z","uid":53026,"like":6,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"239548d5bc5e5ccf189e5dcd39ad1b2691183f8f","tid":819083,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:01:03.000Z","msg":"澳女童拒為國歌站立惹議<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20180914/s00060/49bf29e7b6e2e940ff502eaa902922af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20180914%2Fs00060%2F49bf29e7b6e2e940ff502eaa902922af.jpg&h=1ded38c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1之1<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】澳洲一名9歲女童上周五（7日）當學校奏國歌時，拒絕站立，認為部分歌詞不尊重原住民，事後遭留堂處分。事件引起全國熱議，有右翼政客要求踢女童出校。<br />\n<br />\n右翼政客促踢出校<br />\n<br />\n女童尼爾森 （Harper Nielsen，圖）周三受訪稱，她認為國歌《前進澳洲美之國》（Advance Australia Fair）忽視當地原住民，「當它（歌詞）說前進澳洲美之國，意指前進的白人，當它說『我們很年輕』時，它完全無視比我們早來這裏5萬年的澳洲原住民。」<br />\n<br />\n尼爾森的舉動遭到右翼政客抨擊，右翼參議員漢森（Pauline Hanson）批評尼爾森是「頑童」，主張趕她出校。昆士蘭省影子教育部長布萊傑（Jarrod Bleijie）炮轟尼爾森的父母利用女兒作政治棋子，指摘尼爾森的示威「愚蠢」，認為她拒絕站立不尊重國家，若繼續這樣做，應被勒令停學。<br />\n<br />\n尼爾森的父親則大讚女兒表現出非凡勇氣，希望她能堅持信念，做正確之事。<br />\n<br />\n（衛報）"},{"pid":"c90db781bfc1a38b1298ce3aee06ed3308df3023","tid":819083,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:05:05.000Z","msg":"跪咪得囉，洗Q唔企咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d550d0d4d48da051763fd8b38daee2d74494f0a3","tid":819083,"uid":164913,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:07:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec2ee559ec042f3122d2fd17920fa67f13d531bb","tid":819083,"uid":180026,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:09:00.000Z","msg":"澳洲政治同強國一樣咁黑暗"},{"pid":"49dfc5fc547d9e040e7d513a8a4f822784f12f15","tid":819083,"uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:15:08.000Z","msg":"收到消息,美國都有個小學生拒絕奏國歌時肅立,仲打到上聯邦法院,結果令人感動<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vlBsowohiCw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvlBsowohiCw&d=jtxzMWEAjToVXpklrv0%2FE54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ce65ae44\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vlBsowohiCw</a><br />\n06:19開始"},{"pid":"709c3dccb54429210c4aa358ea686e023e8b56a8","tid":819083,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:32:46.000Z","msg":"Believe in something, even if it means sacrificing everything"},{"pid":"ca8926b5914e2052a04b7408025d06a0c9a2a31a","tid":819083,"uid":153689,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:32:54.000Z","msg":"班右翼講嘢同中共一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef3f85c1761720a33a500533cf3a5623afa2f11","tid":819083,"uid":54721,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ca8926b5914e2052a04b7408025d06a0c9a2a31a","tid":819083,"uid":153689,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:32:54.000Z","msg":"班右翼講嘢同中共一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:35:19.000Z","msg":"中共係極右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419b7b97659de6eaa4ad813257643cccf04694e5","tid":819083,"uid":143241,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:39:44.000Z","msg":"愛國呢個行為好on9"},{"pid":"2b7ff3bfa243f0af168da9fdef810521c86430e7","tid":819083,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"419b7b97659de6eaa4ad813257643cccf04694e5","tid":819083,"uid":143241,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:39:44.000Z","msg":"愛國呢個行為好on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T02:21:32.000Z","msg":"叫人愛國都唔緊要，問題係咩叫愛國先？"},{"pid":"c5c7d8ae9dae02dfcfaf60de3ef19e0ba42b4ab8","tid":819083,"uid":121146,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2